{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013gZkuf3vKvT4ajhbpVh3Su","type":"tool_result","content":"# Plage de Saint-Jorioz\n\n**Municipality:** Saint-Jorioz\n\n**Entrance Fee:** The beach has variable pricing. According to the page: \"Placený vstup v červenci a srpnu (2,60 €), zbytek roku zdarma\" — meaning paid entry during July and August at €2.60, with free access the rest of the year.\n\n**Related Links:**\n- Route/Directions: Google Maps link to the beach\n- Official website: https://saint-jorioz.fr/fr/rb/1110735/decouvrir-la-plage\n\n**Additional Details:** The page describes it as \"Velká přírodní písčitá pláž na Lac d'Annecy s výhledem na Dents de Lanfon\" (a large natural sandy beach on Lake Annecy with views of the Dents de Lanfon) and notes it holds a Blue Flag award."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4a05f5eb-5415-4c0f-bc81-076106e74329","uuid":"7f8ceb4a-5d01-4654-a889-19f7e4d01353","timestamp":"2026-07-04T23:32:42.671Z","tool_use_result":{"bytes":160440,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Plage de Saint-Jorioz\n\n**Municipality:** Saint-Jorioz\n\n**Entrance Fee:** The beach has variable pricing. According to the page: \"Placený vstup v červenci a srpnu (2,60 €), zbytek roku zdarma\" — meaning paid entry during July and August at €2.60, with free access the rest of the year.\n\n**Related Links:**\n- Route/Directions: Google Maps link to the beach\n- Official website: https://saint-jorioz.fr/fr/rb/1110735/decouvrir-la-plage\n\n**Additional Details:** The page describes it as \"Velká přírodní písčitá pláž na Lac d'Annecy s výhledem na Dents de Lanfon\" (a large natural sandy beach on Lake Annecy with views of the Dents de Lanfon) and notes it holds a Blue Flag award.","durationMs":4496,"url":"https://loisirs74.fr/cs/"}}
